methods.addSource:
Add a column location for consideration when constructing groupings.

:param columnLocation: (io.deephaven.engine.table.impl.locations.ColumnLocation) - The column location to add
:param locationRowSetInTable: (io.deephaven.engine.rowset.RowSet) - The location's RowSet in the table

text:
Interface for GroupingProviders that operate on metadata derived from a ColumnLocation for a given
 RowSet key range.
